      "role": "user",
      "content": "a week feels way too short though... i feel like i really need to replenish my stores properly. if i do the 50k dose for like 8 weeks straight to make sure i'm fully optimized, is there really any risk of it being too much? i dont have any health issues or anything, just want to feel better.",
